# ====================================================================
# Microchip Studio (Atmel Studio) Git Ignore Template
# ====================================================================

# --- Build Artifacts ---
# Exclude the entire Debug and Release directories where hex/elf/obj files live
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
*.bin
*.hex
*.eep
*.elf
*.lss
*.map
*.sym
*.o
*.d

# --- Microchip / Atmel Studio User-Specific Files ---
# These store layout data, open tabs, and machine-specific tool paths
*.atsuo
*.suo
*.user
.atmelstart/
Device_Startup/Backup/

# --- Visual Studio Shell Metadata / Caches ---
.vs/
*.ncb
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# --- Backup and Temporary Files ---
*.bak
*~